<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٩٩ ... سُورَةُ الزَّلْزَلَةِ ... آياتها ٨ مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زُلْزِلَتِ}</span> ... رُجَّتْ وَحُرِّكَتْ بِقُوَّةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زِلْزَالَهَا}</span> ... تَحْرِيكَهَا الشَّدِيدَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَثْقَالَهَا}</span> ... مَا فِي بَطْنِهَا مِنَ المَوْتَى والكُنُوزِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا لَهَا}</span> ... مَا الَّذِي حَدَثَ لَهَا؟<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُحَدِّثُ أَخْبَارَهَا}</span> ... تُخْبِرُ الأَرْضُ بِمَا عُمِلَ عَلَيْهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِأَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَوْحَى لَهَا}</span> ... بِسَبَبِ أَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَمَرَهَا بِأَنْ تُخْبِرَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَصْدُرُ النَّاسُ}</span> ... يَرْجِعُونَ عَنْ مَوْقِفِ الِحسَابِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَشْتَاتًا}</span> ... أَصْنافًا مُتَفَرِّقِينَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِّيُرَوْا أَعْمَالَهُمْ}</span> ... لِيُرِيَهُمُ اللهُ مَا عَمِلُوا، وَيُجَازِيَهُمْ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ}</span> ... وَزْنَ نَمْلَةٍ صَغِيرَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>